Texts.Chs: 一套可爱的茶具，非常适合你的茶话会客人。
Texts.Eng: A cutesy tea set, perfect for your plushie tea party guests.

Texts.Chs: 一个令人愉快的挑逗。茶现在听起来很可爱，实际上。
Texts.Eng: A delightful teaser. Tea sounds lovely right about now, actually.

Texts.Chs: 用来泡茶的水壶。我不喜欢这些东西，但是这个茶壶做得很好。
Texts.Eng: A kettle for serving tea. I don't care for the stuff, but the teapot is nicely made.

Texts.Chs: 一套可爱的淡色的小茶具。
Texts.Eng: A small tea set in adorable pastel colors.

Texts.Chs: 叶族人会尽力克克制破破破坏坏的欲望。
Texts.Eng: Floran will ressist urge to sssmash.

Texts.Chs: 哎呀，多可爱的一套茶具啊! 不过我觉得这些茶杯对我的手来说太小了...
Texts.Eng: My, what a darling little tea set! I think the cups are too small for my hands, though...
Some dainty little teapots an' such.

Texts.Chs: 茶话会时间! ... 虽然我实际上没有任何茶...
Texts.Eng: Tea party time! ... Although I don't actually have any tea...
